  <brief_title>The Effect of Intraoperative Magnesium Sulfate Infusion on the Occurrence of Emergence Agitation</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Intraoperative Magnesium Sulfate Infusion on the Occurrence of Emergence Agitation After Pediatric Ophthalmic Surgery</official_title>
  <sponsors>
